cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this harness in research on AI-assisted software engineering,
  deterministic agent guardrails, or provenance-verified code generation,
  please cite it as below.
type: software
title: tauri-postgres-agent-harness
abstract: >-
  A deterministic agent harness for Tauri 2 + React 19 + Hono + Drizzle /
  Postgres 16 pnpm monorepos shipped as signed Windows executables: Claude
  Code hooks that gate turn completion on a green validation chain,
  security-invariant lint rules and pre-write guards, row-level-security
  isolation tests against real Postgres, Tauri capability/CSP policy gates,
  an inline-citation provenance pipeline, and supply-chain-hardened CI across
  both the npm and crates ecosystems.
authors:
  - name: Cogvera Labs
repository-code: 'https://github.com/BhodiSea/tauri-postgres-agent-harness'
license: Apache-2.0
